commit_message:
Add files via upload

Perl script for creating UCSC track hub with a list of bigWig / bigBed files. Creates a separate hub every time it is run. For creating multiple super tracks in a single hub, rerun the script with the various lists of files. The hub files are recreated, but they work as long as the genome and version are the same.

Write-ExcelFiles

Python script that will take the annotated tables (from R script) and convert them into an excel -- one sheet per annot file.

AnnotationRScript

R script for basic annotation of ChIP-seq NarrowPeaks
